==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sunless
<hw>Sun"less</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Destitute or deprived
of the sun or its rays; shaded; shadowed.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The sunken glen whose <qex>sunless</qex> shrubs must weep.</q>
<rj><qau>Byron.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sunlight</ent>⟦br⟧
